                        quê eidem legaliter pertinent tam apostolico privilegio quam imperiali
                        rescripto, tam infra <rs key="#Islands">insulam</rs> Pomposiam quam extra
                        eamdem in <placeName key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/3559"><geogName
                                key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#estates/2454">Laco
                            Sancto</geogName></placeName> et in <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/594"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/2423">Ravennati</geogName></placeName> et in <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/3515"><geogName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#estates/2459">Liviensi</geogName></placeName> et <placeName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/3513"><geogName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#estates/2458">Faventino</geogName></placeName> et in aliis
                        comitatibus, cum <rs key="#Plebs">plebibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">sediminibus</rs>, <rs key="#Castle"
                            >castris</rs>, <rs key="#Churches">capellis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">terris cultis et incultis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs>, <rs key="#Rivers">stillariis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Oil">olivetis</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>, <rs key="#Natural_landscape"
                            >planiciis</rs>, <rs key="#Natural_landscape">ripis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">venationibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rivers #Lakes #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">aquis aquarum
                            discursibus</rs>, <rs key="#Saltworks">salinis</rs>, <rs>salariis</rs>
                        <rs>vinetisque</rs>, <rs key="#Rent_in_kind #Rent_in_money">pensionibus</rs>
                        et <rs key="#Levies #Public_exactions">exhibitionibus</rs> sibi
                        pertinentibus, et ipsum monasterium cum omni sua pertinentia sub <rs
                            key="#Immunity">imperiali defensione</rs> recipit et confirmat quicquid
                        de rebus sororicidê <persName ref="#people/1579">Petri Sigeçonis</persName>
                        condam de <persName><name ref="Accadeo">Accadeo</name></persName> filii in
                        eius imperii dominium devolutis habuit. Apparet bulla cum sigillo plombeo
                        appenso. Incipiens: In nomine sanctê et individuê Trinitatis. Anno Domini
                        MXIIII, dat. XI kal. iunii, indictione XIIa, in <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/90">Sancti
                            Çenonis</orgName> suburbio <placeName ref="#places/59"
                            >Veronê</placeName>.</ab>
